## 6. UX Flows — Parcours Utilisateur

### 6.1 Flow complet : Soumission → Vote → Dispute → Finalisation

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    START([Researcher]) --> ENCRYPT["1. Chiffrement AES-256-GCM\n(client-side)"]
    ENCRYPT --> UPLOAD["2. Upload vers IPFS\n(payload chiffré)"]
    UPLOAD --> SUBMIT["3. submitReport()\n+ verrouillage stake"]
    SUBMIT --> QUEUE[File d'attente comité]
    
    QUEUE --> VOTE{"4. Vote Phase 1\n(K-of-N)"}
    VOTE -->|"≥ K accept"| ACCEPTED[Accepté]
    VOTE -->|"≥ K reject"| REJECTED[Rejeté]
    VOTE -->|"SLA expiré"| ESCALATE["5. triggerEscalation()"]
    
    REJECTED --> DISPUTE{"6. raiseDispute()\n(+ appeal bond)"}
    ESCALATE --> CR
    DISPUTE --> CR["7. Commit-Reveal"]
    
    subgraph "Commit-Reveal (2 phases)"
        CR --> COMMIT["Phase Commit\nhash(vote + salt)"]
        COMMIT -->|deadline| REVEAL["Phase Reveal\nvote + salt"]
    end
    
    REVEAL --> RESOLVE["8. resolveDispute()"]
    RESOLVE -->|"accept ≥ K"| ACCEPTED
    RESOLVE -->|"reject ≥ K"| REJECTED2[Rejeté définitif]
    
    ACCEPTED --> FINALIZE["9. finalizeReport()"]
    REJECTED2 --> FINALIZE
    
    FINALIZE -->|Accepté| PAY["Reward → Researcher\nStake → Refunded"]
    FINALIZE -->|Rejeté| SLASH["Stake → Treasury\nSlashed"]
    
    style ACCEPTED fill:#2d6a4f,color:#fff
    style REJECTED fill:#7b1d1d,color:#fff
    style REJECTED2 fill:#7b1d1d,color:#fff
    style PAY fill:#2d6a4f,color:#fff
    style SLASH fill:#7b1d1d,color:#fff
```

